# API Test Automation with Newman & GitHub Actions

## Tech Stack
- Postman
- Newman
- GitHub Actions
- Allure Reports

## Test Coverage
- Smoke Tests
- Regression Tests
- Contract Validation
- Performance Checks

## How to Run Locally
```bash
newman run collections/ReqRes_API_Testing.postman_collection.json \
  -e environments/QA.sample.postman_environment.json
